\newcommand{\ipc}{Logical. If \code{IndividualsPerColumn=TRUE} then the first argument indicates a (SNPs \eqn{\times} Individ) matrix. Otherwise, the first argument  indicates a (Individ \eqn{\times} SNPs) matrix, which will be  transposed before storage.}
